_sText:
This was a map request, the map is much different than the original design, but it uses the same idea.

This map was made to be uneque, because you can go in any of the 5 rooms to fight, or you can go into the large arena to fight.

This map looks like it may be difficult to use from the pictures, but if you try it out ingame it will be much easier.

Sorry for fullbright
I was trying to get as little lag as possible since this map is made for many players.

Sorry there aren't more pictures!
